    <h2 class="mt-2">About CompNations</h2>
    <p>Welcome to CompNations!</p>
    <p>My name is Davy Lungu, a passionate and self-taught programmer dedicated to making data-driven comparisons accessible and understandable. CompNations leverages the robust and comprehensive World Bank API to provide you with accurate and up-to-date statistics for a wide range of countries.</p>

    <h3>What We Do</h3>
    <p>CompNations allows you to easily compare various statistics between two countries. Whether you're interested in economic indicators, social metrics, or environmental data, we provide a user-friendly interface to help you analyze and understand the differences and similarities between nations. Our goal is to make complex data accessible and actionable for everyone, from researchers and students to business professionals and curious minds.</p>

    <h3>Our Data Source</h3>
    <p>All the data on CompNations is sourced from the World Bank API, ensuring that you receive reliable and authoritative information. The World Bank is a trusted global institution that collects and disseminates a wealth of data on numerous topics, ranging from economic performance to social progress and environmental sustainability. Data is mainly from 1990 to 2022</p>

    <h3>Why Choose CompNations?</h3>
