      <li><strong>Comprehensive Comparisons:</strong> Our platform covers a wide range of statistics, giving you a holistic view of the countries you are comparing.</li>
      <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> We prioritize ease of use, allowing you to quickly find and compare the data you need.</li>
      <li><strong>Customizable Options:</strong> Select from multiple statistics and customize your comparison to suit your specific needs.</li>
